{"lemma":"عَوَزُ","slug":"عَوَزُ","root":"ع.#.ز","root_slug":"ع-_-ز","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-ز","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30997","n30999","n31000","n31001"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%B2%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30997","headword_ar":"عَوِزَ","root":"Ewz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawazN","text_ar":"عَوَزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, wanting; not found;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not existing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(anything)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was wanted, and desired, but not"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2196},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attainable:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, unattainable; not found;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not existing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  The same verb, inf. n. as above, is also said of flesh, or flesh-meat; [app. signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became wasted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, wanting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not found;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (A;) or the verb thus used is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEowaza","text_ar":"اَعْوَزَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iEowaAzN","text_ar":"اـِعْوَازٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an affair)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, hard, difficult,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strait;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, * TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEwz","text_ar":"اعوز","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, difficult."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKtt.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, poor, needy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indigent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEwz","text_ar":"اعوز","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iEowaAzN","text_ar":"اـِعْوَازٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb;:) or the latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, poor so as to possess nothing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, Msb;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became in want, and in an unsound condition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEwz~","text_ar":"اعوزّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiEowizaAzN","text_ar":"اِعْوِزَازٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in an evil condition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAza Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"عَازَ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEuwzu","text_ar":"يَعُوزُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawozN","text_ar":"عَوْزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wanted, needed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"required, the thing, and found it not."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAzahu Al$~aYo'u","text_ar":"عَازَهُ الشَّىْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEowazahu","text_ar":"اَعْوَزَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", virtually signify the same.] See 4."}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","Lth","A","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n30999","headword_ar":"عَوْزٌ","root":"Ewz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"berries of the grape-vine"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grapes;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEawozu","text_ar":"العَوْزُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being expl. as signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hab~u AlEinabi","text_ar":"حَبُّ العِنَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: n. un. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraTotu AlEunoquwda","text_ar":"خَرَطْتُ العُنْقُودَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEinaba","text_ar":"العِنَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) is expl. by AHeyth as said when one takes, (O,) or strips off, (TA,) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eawoz","text_ar":"عَوْز"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA) that are upon the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Enqwd","text_ar":"عنقود"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or bunch], (O,) or that are upon the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Enb","text_ar":"عنب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or grape-vine], (TA,) with all his fingers, (O, TA,) so as to clear it of its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ewz","text_ar":"عوز"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) or so as to clear them from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euwd","text_ar":"عُود"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or stalk] thereof. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31000","headword_ar":"عَوَزٌ","root":"Ewz","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eawiza","text_ar":"عَوِزَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] (S, O, Msb.) ―         -b2-  [As a simple subst.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Want; need; exigency;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, O, K;) in which sense"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEaAwizu","text_ar":"مَعَاوِزُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be an irreg. pl. thereof similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaAmiHu","text_ar":"مَلَامِحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aAbihu","text_ar":"مَشَابِهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Har p. 26:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"destitution:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poverty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evilness of condition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"littleness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scarceness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scantiness, of a thing, to a person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his estimation, and its needfulness to him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, * Mgh, TA: *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straitness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty, of a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSaAbahu EawazN","text_ar":"اَصَابَهُ عَوَزٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poverty, befell him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidaAdN","text_ar":"سِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino EawazK","text_ar":"مِنْ عَوَزٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Mgh, TA,) a well-known prov., expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sd","text_ar":"سد"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","A","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n31001","headword_ar":"عَوِزٌ","root":"Ewz","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Poor; needy; indigent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, in this art. and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lwz","text_ar":"لوز"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEowizN","text_ar":"مُعْوِزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; (S, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessing little;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in an evil condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEowazN","text_ar":"مِعْوَزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,) which latter is anomalous. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu laEawizN lawizN","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَعَوِزٌ لَوِزٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is poor indeed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the last word being an imitative sequent, (K, in this art. and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lwz","text_ar":"لوز"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and a corroborative. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","TA"]}]}}